main event: On 23 September 1955, a sighting of a dark object, shaped like a toy top, was reported in Leonape, Pennsylvania for a duration of 3-5 minutes.
interesting points: The object was described as dark and resembling a toy top with something underneath it,The sighting lasted between 3 to 5 minutes,No photographs were taken of the object, The object was suspected to possibly be a balloon due to its characteristics and the observations made, The report concludes that the object was likely caused by a weather balloon released earlier that day.
sighted object: dark object shaped like a toy top
witness description: Mrs. Leonape Road, RFD 2, West Chester, Pennsylvania, age 33, housewife with good vision
